layout.p:
Columns: 16;
                                                  ruled lines: 22;
                                                  written lines: 22; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane. Four columns per membrane, each written within decorated engravings.  Two or three tagin on שעטנזגץ, one on בדהיחק, and the letter ח arched throughout. Several majuscular and minuscular letters. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. Wooden rollers (173mm high).
